@Otomar.WebApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:8585

### Login - Get Token First
POST {{Otomar.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@otomar.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Initialize Payment
POST {{Otomar.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/payments/initialize
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "creditCardNumber": "5218487962459752",
  "creditCardExpDateYear": "26",
  "creditCardExpDateMonth": "12",
